node.title: Twelve-year-old boy pleads not guilty to murder of Northland man
node.description: A 12-year-old accused of murdering a man near Kaikohe has pleaded not guilty in the High Court in WhangƒÅrei this morning.
node.content:
["A 12-year-old accused of murdering a man near Kaikohe has pleaded not guilty in the High Court in Whang\u0101rei this morning.", "", "
\nPhoto: Ministry of Justice website\n
", "He was charged last December, after the death of Michael John Biggins in September.", "The 62-year-old was found seriously injured in a crashed vehicle in a paddock in \u014ckaihau.", "The 12-year-old accused, who has name suppression, was remanded in the custody of Oranga Tamariki today.", "He is jointly charged with a 15-year-old boy.", "Their High Court murder trial will start in March next year."]
